You try it.

66
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,680
(Do not touch or eat)

67
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,720
He asked me to lick it.

68
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,640
Why is he so bad?

69
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,840
Hello, everyone. We meet again.

70
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,080
Hello.

71
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,080
(Hu Junxia, President of
the New Zealand-China Tourism Association)

72
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,320
See you again.

73
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:07,040
The Springs we visited before

74
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,720
