75
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,400
Today, we've come to

76
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:12,720
New Zealand's most active

77
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,840
Hell's Gate Geothermal Park.

78
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,680
Okay.

79
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,840
Things become interesting.

80
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,360
Over here,

81
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,800
