natural hot springs,

154
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:25,080
many with fluctuating temperatures.

155
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:28,520
Always follow your guide
and official trails.

156
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,040
Okay.

157
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,840
This is so beautiful.

158
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,440
So pretty.

159
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,160
Oh, my.

160
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,264
Take a photo.

161
00:05:35,264 --> 00:05:37,520
(Gong Jun)

162
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,920
Amazing.

163
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,104
Very beautiful.

164
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,920
This is boiling water.

165
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,000
Eggs would cook right away
if placed here.

166
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,680
It's just like black sesame paste.

167
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:53,920
Black sesame...

168
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,640
(Geothermal hazard.
Do not approach casually)

169
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,488
Have a bite.

170
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,000
It's so hot today.

171
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,400
Lin Yi, how about your long johns?

172
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,680
My thermal top is soaked through.

173
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,600
Your thermal top is soaked through.

174
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,416
I'm already drenched now.

175
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,640
Look at that tree. It looks just like
something out of a comic book,

176
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,680
as if it were drawn by hand.

177
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:08,920
Right?

178
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,640
That one?

179
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,920
That area over there, right?

180
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,640
Plants can even grow in such hot water.

181
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,080
So those plants are amazing.

182
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:16,840
So tenacious.

183
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:17,344
Yes.

184
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,960
Over here, there is a unique pool

185
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:24,040
with temperatures between 85

186
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,440
and 88 degrees

187
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,800
and a pH value of around 6.2.

188
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,200
Food cooked here tastes great.

189
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,200
The water is non-toxic, right?

190
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,320
Non-toxic. Yes.

191
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:33,960
Alright, everyone,

192
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,800
